snippet.title: Snap the Sentinel, First Level - 7DFPS WIP
snippet.description:
EDIT: It's been released @ https://tehrealsalt.itch.io/snap-the-sentinel

Work in progress of Snap the Sentinel, a short standalone Doom-style game for the 7DFPS game jam. This is the first level, Home Base. At the time of writing, 3 out of 5 planned stages have been fully completed.

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/tehrealsalt
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/tehrealsalt

Credits:
TehRealSalt - Programming, graphics, level design, character design
SeventhSentinel - Music, sound effects, level design
Jeck Jims - 3D models
VelocitOni - Character design, graphics
